sions":true,"forks_count":4220,"mirror_url":null,"archived":false,"disabled":false,"open_issues_count":3116,"license":{"key":"apache-2.0","name":"Apache License 2.0","spdx_id":"Apache-2.0","url":"https://api.github.com/licenses/apache-2.0","node_id":"MDc6TGljZW5zZTI="},"allow_forking":true,"is_template":false,"web_commit_signoff_required":false,"topics":["bevy","game-development","game-engine","gamedev","open-source","rust"],"visibility":"public","forks":4220,"open_issues":3116,"watchers":42996,"default_branch":"main","permissions":{"admin":false,"maintain":false,"push":false,"triage":false,"pull":true}},"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/pulls/12105","html_url":"https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/pull/12105","diff_url":"https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/pull/12105.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/pull/12105.patch","merged_at":"2024-02-25T22:52:19Z"},"body":"# Objective\r\n\r\n- Fixes #12068\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\n- Split `bevy_render::color::colorspace` across the various space implementations in `bevy_color` as appropriate.\r\n- Moved `From` implementations involving `bevy_render::color::LegacyColor` into `bevy_render::color`\r\n\r\n## Migration Guide\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::SrgbColorSpace::<f32>::linear_to_nonlinear_srgb`\r\n\r\nUse `bevy_color::color::gamma_function_inverse`\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::SrgbColorSpace::<f32>::nonlinear_to_linear_srgb`\r\n\r\nUse `bevy_color::color::gamma_function`\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::SrgbColorSpace::<u8>::linear_to_nonlinear_srgb`\r\n\r\nModify the `u8` value to instead be an `f32` (`|x| x as f32 / 255.`), use `bevy_color::color::gamma_function_inverse`, and back again.\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::SrgbColorSpace::<u8>::nonlinear_to_linear_srgb`\r\n\r\nModify the `u8` value to instead be an `f32` (`|x| x as f32 / 255.`), use `bevy_color::color::gamma_function`, and back again.\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::HslRepresentation::hsl_to_nonlinear_srgb`\r\n\r\nUse `Hsla`'s implementation of `Into<Srgba>`\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::HslRepresentation::nonlinear_srgb_to_hsl`\r\n\r\nUse `Srgba`'s implementation of `Into<Hsla>`\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::LchRepresentation::lch_to_nonlinear_srgb`\r\n\r\nUse `Lcha`'s implementation of `Into<Srgba>`\r\n\r\n### `bevy_render::color::colorspace::LchRepresentation::nonlinear_srgb_to_lch`\r\n\r\nUse `Srgba`'s implementation of `Into<Lcha>`\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/12105/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/12105/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/comments/1962877339","html_url":"https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/issues/12068#issuecomment-1962877339","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/12068","id":1962877339,"node_id":"IC_kwDODf6-U850_yGb","user":{"login":"CptPotato","id":3957610,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM5NTc2MTA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3957610?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato","html_url":"https://github.com/CptPotato","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/CptPotato/events{/privacy}","received_events_